videos.description: Off a missed basket Indiana pushes the ball up the court and De'ron Davis lays it in.

tracking.trackingName: NCB_One-Play (Indiana scores off the fast break) 2017/11/29 ESHEET

videos.headline: Indiana scores off the fast break

videos.description: Devonte Green gets the steal off Marvin Bagley III and takes it up the court for the alley-oop dunk to Freddie McSwain Jr.

tracking.trackingName: NCB_One-Play (Indiana finishes off break with alley-oop dunk) 2017/11/29 ESHEET

videos.headline: Indiana finishes off break with alley-oop dunk

videos.description: Off the tipped pass, Grayson Allen takes it up the baseline and throws down the dunk.

videos.headline: Allen drives the baseline for a two-handed dunk

videos.description: Wendell Carter Jr. grabs the offensive board and throws down the two-handed dunk.

videos.description: De'Ron Davis throws up a shot against Marvin Bagley III and gets the bounce off the back of the rim to fall plus the foul.

videos.description: Devonte Green bounces a terrific pass to De'Ron Davis who slams the big two-handed dunk.
